messages.message: Looks like rabbitmq was a bit overloaded for the last ~20 minutes and has resolved itself. cc @Andrey

Would love to be able to set up alerts for this, so we can have a heads up before people start complaining that “Refiner/Studio field runs are taking forever” :stuck_out_tongue:

will keep you posted
